name: Deep Within the Temple of the Wolf
localeName: Deep Within the Temple of the Wolf
desc: The Knights of Favonius have been mobilized to contain Stormterror's destruction. Venture forth with Cavalry Captain Kaeya to the Temple of the Wolf and stop Stormterror from gaining the power within.

name: Hidden Teardrop in the Heart of the Jungle
localeName: Hidden Teardrop in the Heart of the Jungle
desc: The party has come to a secret ruin hidden deep in a jungle. One of Dvalin's powerful teardrops lies within. Head inside with Jean and Diluc to track it down.

name: Realm Within
localeName: Realm Within
desc: Realm Within

name: Retrieve the Treasure
localeName: Retrieve the Treasure
desc:
The Abyss Mage has fled into the Domain.
Brave the Domain and retrieve Klee's treasure!

name: The Golden Shadow
localeName: The Golden Shadow
desc:
Your pursuit of the truth brings you to the very heart of the political storm that has been slowly brewing in Liyue Harbor.
It is time to peer beyond the glittering gold, and see what lurks in the shadows...

name: Jade Chamber Storyline
localeName: Jade Chamber Storyline

name: Memories: The Golden Shadow I
localeName: Memories: The Golden Shadow I
desc:
The storm clouds gathering over Liyue have finally parted, and the schemes that once gripped this land have been shattered by the combined efforts of the Qixing, the adepti, and yourself.
Still, the memories of your duel with Childe of the Fatui in the depths of the Golden House remain fresh in your mind.
Relive this duel, and you may yet learn something new...

localeName: Deep Within the Temple of the Falcon
desc: The Knights of Favonius have been mobilized to contain Stormterror's destructive rampage. Venture forth with Amber the Outrider to the Temple of the Falcon and stop Stormterror from gaining the power within.

name: Find the Stolen Book
localeName: Find the Stolen Book
desc: The thief seems to be hiding inside this ruin...

name: Deep Within the Temple of the Lion
localeName: Deep Within the Temple of the Lion
desc: The Knights of Favonius have been mobilized to contain Stormterror's destruction. Venture forth with Lisa the Librarian to the Temple of the Lion and stop Stormterror from gaining the power within.

name: Hunt Down the Abyss Mage
localeName: Hunt Down the Abyss Mage
desc:
The Abyss Mage has disappeared somewhere deep inside this underground ruin.
Do not spare this evildoer.

name: Retrieve the Holy Lyre der Himmel
localeName: Retrieve the Holy Lyre der Himmel
desc:
The treasure of Mondstadt and the power of the Anemo Archon will not simply be handed over quietly.
Defeat the guards inside and take back the Holy Lyre der Himmel.

name: Secret Ingredient
localeName: Secret Ingredient
desc:
Xiangling is sure that the ingredient she's looking for is hidden somewhere in the depths of this domain.
So fight your way to the far end and retrieve it â€” if you've got the guts!

name: The Great Adventurer Stanley
localeName: The Great Adventurer Stanley
desc: Ellin asked you to search for the greenhorn adventurer Jack within the Temple of the Lion. It seems he is traveling together with the legendary adventurer, Stanley.

name: Another Detour
localeName: Another Detour
desc:
Despite consulting her notebook, Qiqi dashes into the ruins for reasons unknown.
You've heard that it's dangerous in there. Catch up to her and ensure her safety.

name: Karma-Heavy Cavern
localeName: Karma-Heavy Cavern
desc: This place attracts monsters corrupted by sinister energy. According to Xiao, their mutation might be connected to his karmic debt...

name: Cloud Retainer's Abode
localeName: Cloud Retainer's Abode
desc: Herein lies the abode of Cloud Retainer. The adeptus desires not to see guests, and the way is shut. A lack of care for where one lays their head is common among all who live. Do you truly wish to enter?

name: The Wonderful World Of Mr. Cyclops
localeName: The Wonderful World Of Mr. Cyclops
desc:
Though it was agreed to let Teucer visit the "Institute for Toy Research"...
The toughest battles are not fought against a redoubtable foe but in defense of a child's innocence.

name: Of Mysteries and Salt
localeName: Of Mysteries and Salt
desc:
The seal has been broken, and both the treasures and the tale of the God of Salt await within.
The party pushes on, each armed with disparate aims...

name: Cloud Retainer's Abode
localeName: Cloud Retainer's Abode
desc: Herein lies the abode of Cloud Retainer. The adeptus desires not to see guests, and the way is shut. A lack of care for where one lays their head is common among all who live. Do you truly wish to enter?

name: Enter the "border"
localeName: Enter the "border"
desc:
After sufficient preparation, you follow Hu Tao into the mysterious "border."
 Remember her warning and don't make a fuss about anything that waits ahead.

name: Deserted Ruins of Thermadon
localeName: Deserted Ruins of Thermadon
desc: Recently discovered underground ruins. Even though the Guild keeps warning of the dangers hidden inside, nothing can go wrong with Bennett by your side, right?

name: Deserted Ruins of Eya
localeName: Deserted Ruins of Eya
desc: Recently discovered underground ruins. Even though the Guild has repeatedly expressed safety concerns about venturing inside, nothing can go wrong with Bennett by your side, right?

name: Abyssal Traces
localeName: Abyssal Traces
desc: The abyssal traces have led you back here. Will the Abyss Herald rear its head and let you witness its transformation brought upon by the Abyssal Gospel?

name: Lost Treasure of Arcadia
localeName: Lost Treasure of Arcadia
desc: Lost treasures reveal themselves only to those with true wisdom. Having solved the mystery of Arcadia, you finally arrive at the site of the treasure...

name: Storming Terror
localeName: Storming Terror
desc: After a long and daring pursuit of Dvalin, who has been led astray by the Abyss Mages, you are about to finally confront him once and for all.

name: Cipher for the Ciphertext
localeName: Cipher for the Ciphertext
desc:
A ciphertext written by an Abyss Mage for an Abyss Mage.
The simplest way to read it is to find an Abyss Mage, of course...

name: The Reward for Courage is Flight
localeName: The Reward for Courage is Flight
desc:
Raptor is lurking somewhere deep inside this temple. You cannot let him escape again.
Use what you've learned about gliding to take him down.

name: The Reward for Courage is Flight
localeName: The Reward for Courage is Flight
desc:
Raptor is lurking somewhere deep inside this temple. You cannot let him escape again.
Use what you've learned about gliding to take him down.

name: Ascend: Clear the Ruins
localeName: Ascend: Clear the Ruins
desc:
A huge number of monsters established their camp in the ruins, threatening the safety of the area. 
Defeat them all to prove your courage to the Adventurers' Guild.

name: Memories: Storming Terror I
localeName: Memories: Storming Terror I
desc:
Now that the Stormterror crisis has passed, it's clear skies above Mondstadt once again.
However, the memory of facing Dvalin in the sky amidst the storms is ever so vivid.
Relive your memories and once again partake in the battle. Maybe you'll learn something new.

name: Explore: Fallen Fortress
localeName: Explore: Fallen Fortress
desc: Deep in the ruins, you discovered an ancient fortress occupied by monsters. You'll need to go deeper if you want to find the treasure...

name: Trial: Scorching Fire and Raging Lightning
localeName: Trial: Scorching Fire and Raging Lightning
desc: In these ruins you discover a now destroyed training ground belonging to an ancient civilization. To pass this trial, you need to take hold of vicious fire and crackling lightning to take down your enemy.

name: Explore: Windy Cliff
localeName: Explore: Windy Cliff
desc: Though it lies deep underground, the strong winds filled every corridor of the ruin. Don't be discouraged! Find the treasure deep within the ruin!

name: Investigate: Secret Hideout
localeName: Investigate: Secret Hideout
desc:
These ruins show signs of monster activity.
This threat cannot go unaddressed if Mondstadt is to remain safe.

name: Explore: Travels of the Moonlit Venturer
localeName: Explore: Travels of the Moonlit Venturer
desc: Beneath the labyrinth lies the unexplored Moonlit Wonderland, a trove of pots and kettles. Search for what hidden treasures await discovery there.

name: Explore: Tarry Among the Peach Blossoms
localeName: Explore: Tarry Among the Peach Blossoms
desc: This place was once a paradise from someone's dreams. Search through its former bountiful blossoms and restore peace to the land once more.

name: Explore: Voyage to the Sanguine Sky
localeName: Explore: Voyage to the Sanguine Sky
desc: This is the Realm of Clouds. Guizhong, its former ruler, acquired several ancient and evil artifacts during her research into mechanics. The adepti created this realm to contain them.

name: Explore: Lucky Encounter in the Clouds
localeName: Explore: Lucky Encounter in the Clouds
desc: Only by a stroke of luck may one chance upon this paradise enveloped by clouds and mist. Though it appears serene from the outside, there is peril to be found within.

name: Elemental Trial: Vaporize
localeName: Elemental Trial: Vaporize
desc: Master the Vaporize reaction using Hydro and Pyro through this challenge.

name: Elemental Trial: Melt
localeName: Elemental Trial: Melt
desc: Master the Melt reaction using Pyro and Cryo through this challenge.

name: Elemental Trial: Overloaded
localeName: Elemental Trial: Overloaded
desc: Master the Overloaded reaction using Pyro and Electro through this challenge.

name: Elemental Trial: Superconduct
localeName: Elemental Trial: Superconduct
desc: Master the Superconduct reaction using Cryo and Electro through this challenge.

name: Elemental Trial: Electro-Charged
localeName: Elemental Trial: Electro-Charged
desc: Master the Electro-Charged reaction using Electro and Hydro through this challenge.

name: Elemental Trial: Frozen
localeName: Elemental Trial: Frozen
desc: Master the Frozen reaction using Cryo and Hydro through this challenge.

name: Elemental Trial: Crystallize
localeName: Elemental Trial: Crystallize
desc: Master the Crystallize reaction between Geo and Hydro, Pyro, Cryo and Electro through this challenge.

name: Elemental Trial: Swirl
localeName: Elemental Trial: Swirl
desc: Master the Swirl reaction between Anemo and Hydro, Pyro, Cryo and Electro through this challenge.

desc: In this stage, enemies will come in from two different directions. If you wish to achieve victory, you must figure out a way to fend this pincer attack off...

localeName: Three Stars Tussle for the Spotlight: Difficulty 4
desc: In this stage, enemies will keep pouring in from three different directions. If you wish to achieve victory, you must decide which lane to tackle first...

name: Beauty Withers Hither While Truth Dithers Thither: Difficulty 5
localeName: Beauty Withers Hither While Truth Dithers Thither: Difficulty 5
desc: In this stage, you must prevent enemies from reaching either of two different locations. Masterful placement of Veneficus Mechanici, perhaps, is the key to victory...

desc: In this stage, enemies may travel by a different route to trick you. Figuring out their intended destination may yet pave the road to victory...
